T01TD1157E:203a-1: gu na aa paryanta sto tra ba tu k'a ri k'a /
T01TD1157E:203a-3: yon tan mtha' yas par bstod pa'i don gyi tshig le'ur byas pa /
T01TD1157E:203a-5: yon tan mi shes sgro dag dang //
T01TD1157E:203a-6: nga rgyal med dang 'dod don bsgrub //
T01TD1157E:203a-7: tshigs bcad don bzhi ldan pa yis //
T01TD1157E:203a-8: bstod pa'i gleng ni bslang ba bstan //
T01TD1157E:203a-9: rgyu dang 'bras bu gzhan don gyis //
T01TD1157E:203a-10: bstod pa'i don rnams thams cad bsdus //
T01TD1157E:203a-11: de la dang po byang chub rgyu //
T01TD1157E:203a-12: 'bras bu sems can don nyid bstan //
T01TD1157E:203a-13: bstan pa sbyor ba dbang mdzad pa'i //
T01TD1157E:203a-14: gnas skabs gsum gyis rgyu bstan to //
T01TD1157E:203a-15: gzhan don byang chub smon lam gyi //
T01TD1157E:203a-16: rang bzhin gyis ni bsam pa ste //
T01TD1157E:203a-17: tshigs bcad lnga dang lnga rnams kyis //
T01TD1157E:203a-18: de'i rgyu bzhi dang bcas pa bstan //
T01TD1157E:203a-20: grogs dang longs spyod byas pas bstan //
T01TD1157E:203a-21: rigs dang dge bshes snying rje dang //
T01TD1157E:203a-22: skyon med bsams pa gnyis kyi rgyu //
T01TD1157E:203a-23: de min de nyid sar gnas pas //
T01TD1157E:203a-24: 'dir ni sbyor ba rnam gnyis byas //
T01TD1157E:203a-25: snga ma'i pha rol phyin pa bcu //
T01TD1157E:203a-26: gzhan gyi pha rol phyin pa bdun //
T01TD1157E:203a-27: tshigs bcad drug gis drug rnams ston //
T01TD1157E:203a-28: gnyis kyis gcig yin gsum gyis gzhan //
T01TD1157E:203a-29: dang po'i khyad par bsam pa dang //
T01TD1157E:203a-30: sbyor ba len pa sbyin bya ba'o //
T01TD1157E:203a-31: dang po lnga ni re re yis //
T01TD1157E:203a-32: zag med gzhan ni gnyis kyis so //
T01TD1157E:203a-33: nyon mongs pa dang skye dang las //
T01TD1157E:203a-34: thabs dang rab tu smin bya ba //
T01TD1157E:203a-35: dbang mdzad lnga ni dgos bcas par //
T01TD1157E:203a-36: gnyis gnyis gnyis gnyis gsum gyis so //
T01TD1157E:203a-37: de la kha cig dngos ma gsungs //
T01TD1157E:203a-38: mi mthun phyogs zad pa la yin //
T01TD1157E:203a-39: 'bras bu gsum ste byang chub dang //
T01TD1157E:203a-40: nyes dang yon tan spangs 'byor ba'o //
T01TD1157E:203a-41: gzhan don gsum ste chos bstan dang //
T01TD1157E:203a-42: dam nyam pa dang yun ring gnas //
T01TD1157E:203a-43: thams yongs su bsngo ba ste //
T01TD1157E:203a-44: bstod pa'i don ni bsdus pa bstan //
T01TD1157E:203a-45: yon tan mtha' yas par bstod pa'i don gyi tshig le'ur byas pa slob dpon chen po phyogs kyi glang pos mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1157E:203a-47: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po sarba dznya de ba dang /
T01TD1157E:203b-0: lo ts'a ba @203b bande rin chen mchog gis bsgyur /
T01TD1157E:203b-1: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande dpal brtsegs rakshi tas zhus nas gtan la phab pa'o//
